{"tid":900604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗徒手接網球失敗！女友不幸被擊中...","createTime":"2018-11-13T11:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T17:42:46.000Z","uid":20634,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e945103ff6e9af8b48d5990907a72aa589d616b2","tid":900604,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/11/13/e/ee316fcc037bff8ddfb7e7b56e55c281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2Fe%2Fee316fcc037bff8ddfb7e7b56e55c281.jpg&h=a869784f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC.朗拿度想在女友面前秀一下，結果.....<br />\n<br />\n　　《太陽報》消息，祖雲達斯球星C.朗拿度觀看網球比賽時，<span style=\"color: red;\">試圖表演</span>徒手接網球，但沒有接住。<br />\n<br />\n　　近日C.朗拿度來到倫敦O2球場，和女友喬治娜、兒子「小C.朗」一起觀看ATP比賽。<br />\n<br />\n　　這是一場頭號種子選手祖高域的比賽，C.朗拿度坐在了最前排。即使在網球比賽中，C.朗拿度也成為焦點，網球飛向他時，他試圖表演徒手接球，但沒有抓住，球擊中了喬治娜的頭。<br />\n<br />\n　　隨後他把球撿起來，扔回了場內，並摸摸「小C.朗」的頭，然後一家三口開起了玩笑。網民「抽水」稱：「看來C.朗拿度真做不到門將。」<br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度是一名忠實的網球粉絲，世界盃前，他去法網現場為拿度加油助威。"},{"pid":"878602967421d215aff7a4e1385cc7bfc507b5bf","tid":900604,"uid":174013,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"渣唔慣細波"},{"pid":"014dad9fbdcda9b01e18a7ee241d0b238eb51074","tid":900604,"uid":294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"成個劉馬車咁"},{"pid":"44000917bb87b5d91c5eb41c64f9813a6431737d","tid":900604,"uid":3454,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"014dad9fbdcda9b01e18a7ee241d0b238eb51074","tid":900604,"uid":294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"成個劉馬車咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙劉馬車"},{"pid":"a31cc4c9229751eda85cedf83f129ebee01cf408","tid":900604,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"761698bb1ddebef47d735c394ce8ca7140517c13","tid":900604,"u